  {
    question: "Do you offer warranties on your work?",
    answer:
      "Yes, we stand behind our craftsmanship with solid warranties. Our artificial turf installations come with a 10-year warranty, and we offer varying warranty periods for other services. We'll discuss specific warranty details during your consultation.",
